{"title":"望子速归","authors":["刘王立明"],"dates":[{"year":1946,"month":6,"day":13}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"望子速归"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘王立明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三四年前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了家仇国恨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在参议会里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾建议征用知识青年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一面以身作则命二子从军——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小的投成都中央军校，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大的入陆军机械化学校于滇南双江镇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去年毕业了一个，敌人业已投降，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然军规森严，仍旧是奉命长征！？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前程万里，去与死亡搏斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一阵心寒，别时禁不住全家热泪抛滚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"霎时即抵万里长城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"关外满处冰雪冷气逼人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四周逼人民为敌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片厮杀之声！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打虎山上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家书被扣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"游子思亲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想不到胜利后尚有这样的怪行！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千百万母亲思子成疾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东北更需要和平，安定！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望儿速归重相逢！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":2,"page_end":2}